item.title: Noah Clements Honored with Florida Bar President’s Pro Bono Service Award
item.dc:creator: Noah Clements
item.description:
On January 27, Noah Clements was honored with the Florida Bar President’s Pro Bono Service Award for the out-of-state division.  Many thanks to Sidley Austin for the opportunities.

The post Noah Clements Honored with Florida Bar President’s Pro Bono Service Award appeared first on The Clements Firm.
